data.description: This quaint home is nestled in a great location, close to a nice park (festival of lights park) and sits on a full acre. There are lots of beautiful, mature trees located on the property, the backyard is basically completely shaded. There are 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 good sized full bathrooms. You will love the original wood flooring consistent throughout the home. The kitchen is open to the living room and dining room creating the desired open concept layout. The water heater is brand new. Insulation was installed in the attic in 2022. There will be several improvements made prior to closing. The following improvements have been made, removing the wooden front porch and ramp then adding in railing on either side of the front porch steps, flooring in both bathrooms will be replaced to made more sturdy, flooring in both dining room and kitchen will be replaced to be made more sturdy, back bedroom flooring will be repaired as needed, hot water heater closet door will be replaced, front door threshold will be replaced, and the entire interior of the home will be painted. This home will be sold "as is" following the improvements listed above. More pictures coming soon, this property is a MUST SEE.
